PageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 31, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zks1720074466587.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zks1720074466587.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zks1720074466587.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cfj1665702607852\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__help_223724\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Display help information, either a Uniface help message or information from the native help system.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__topic_d73430e1_d73431e1_d73432e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73433e1_d73434e1_d73435e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span> (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/id</span> | <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/topic</span> | <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/keyword</span>) <var class=\"keyword varname\">Parameters</var> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/noborder</span>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73436e1_d73437e1_d73438e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/noborder</span>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">HelpMessage</var>\n               {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">VertPos</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span><var class=\"keyword varname\">HorizPos</var>\n               {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">VertSize</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span><var class=\"keyword varname\">HorizSize</var>}}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73439e1_d73440e1_d73441e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help/id</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Topic</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ChmFile</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73442e1_d73443e1_d73444e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help/topic</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Topic</var> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span><var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalName</var>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73445e1_d73446e1_d73447e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help/keyword</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Keyword</var> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span><var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalName</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__topic_d48282e1_d48283e1_d48284e1_d48285e1_d48286e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d251581e156\">Qualifiers</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Qualifiers</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1__entry__1\">\n Qualifier\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/id</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1__entry__2\"> Retrieves and displays an online help topic in\n                        a CHM file based on its numeric context ID. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/topic</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1__entry__2\"> Retrieves and displays an online help topic,\n                        index, or table of contents from the native help system. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/keyword</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1__entry__2\"> Retrieves and displays help about a keyword\n                        from a WinHelp file. <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__note_w1613ab1b7b5b3b3b7b5b3b1_w1614ab1b7b5b3b3b7b5b3_w1615ab1b7b5b3b3b7b5_w1616ab1b7b5b3b3b7_w1617ab1b7b5b3b3_w1618ab1b7b5b3_w1619ab1b7b5_w1620ab1b7_w1621ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> WinHelp is an obsolete help system.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/noborder</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6716e1_d6717e1_d6718e1__entry__2\">\n In character mode, displays the form window for USYS:USYSTXT without a border.\n <p class=\"p\">The switch is ignored in GUI mode and in server page components.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__topic_d48287e1_d48288e1_d48289e1_d48290e1_d48291e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d251581e244\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Topic</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__3\">\n Help topic identifier. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">Topic</var> is an empty string (\"\"), the index or table of contents for the native help is displayed.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__3\"> Location of the help file as specified in the\n                        initialization file. If omitted or not found in the initialization file, the\n                        logical name <code class=\"ph codeph\">DEFAULT</code> is used. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Keyword</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__3\">\n Keyword that maps to a topic. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">Keyword</var> is an empty string (\"\") or is not found, the native help engine displays an error message.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">HelpMessage</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__3\">\n Help message text. Often, the function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span> is used, referring to a global help text or message.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">VertPos</var>, <var class=\"keyword varname\">HorizPos</var>, <var class=\"keyword varname\">VertSize</var>, and <var class=\"keyword varname\">HorizSize</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1__entry__3\">\n Position and size of the help form, expressed in character cells. If the help text is larger than the size defined, vertical and horizontal scroll bars appear as needed. By default, the help window appears with a size that exactly fits the help text being displayed. These arguments have no effect in the Web environment.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__topic_d48292e1_d48293e1_d48294e1_d48295e1_d48296e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d251581e379\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values Returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__2\">\n Uniface help form was exited with ^ACCEPT.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__2\">\n Native help successfully started. This value is always returned in the Web environment.\n <p class=\"p\">Uniface help form was left with ^QUIT.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__1\">\n -1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__2\">\n Uniface help form <span class=\"ph filepath\">USYS:USYSTXT.frm</span> could not be found.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__1\">\n -2\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__2\">\n Uniface help form is not correct.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__1\">\n -3\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__2\">\n Unable to start native help.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__1\">\n -4\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__2\"> Platform does not support native help. (If\n                        this case you may want to use the <code class=\"ph codeph\">help</code> statement to provide\n                        help information.) </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__1\">\n -5\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__2\">\n Native help does not support the requested option.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__1\">\n -6\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__2\">\n Unable to map logical name.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__1\">\n -7\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6722e1_d6723e1_d6724e1__entry__2\">\n Requested topic or keyword not found.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 4. </span><span class=\"title\">Values commonly returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__2\">\n Error Constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-350</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UHLPERR_STARTUP&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__3\">\n Unable to start help.\n <p class=\"p\">Uniface form <span class=\"ph filepath\">USYS:USYSTXT.frm</span> is missing or is not correct.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-351</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UHLPERR_PLATFORM&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__3\">\n Platform does not support native help. (In this case you may want to use the help [native] statement to provide help information.)\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-352</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UHLPERR_LOGICAL_NAME&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__3\">\n Unable to map logical name.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-354</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UHLPERR_OPTION&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__3\">\n Native help does not support the requested option.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-353</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UHLPERR_TOPIC&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cfj1665702607852__table_d6725e1_d6726e1_d6727e1__entry__3\">\n Requested help topic or keyword not found.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__topic_d48297e1_d48298e1_d48299e1_d48300e1_d48301e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d251581e673\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__d5909e20\">Use in Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__topic_d48302e1_d48303e1_d48304e1_d48305e1_d48306e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d251581e682\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73466e1_d73467e1_d73468e1\">When used with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/id</span> switch, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span> statement starts the specified Microsoft Help file (<span class=\"ph filepath\">.chm</span>) and displays the help file corresponding to the context ID. When using this switch is used, an initialization file that maps the id to the topic must be provided in the same directory as the CHM file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73472e1_d73473e1_d73474e1\">When used with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/topic</span>, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span> statement starts a native help engine to display the specified information.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73475e1_d73476e1_d73477e1\">When used without a switch or with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/noborders</span>, the help statement displays the specified Uniface help text in an overlay help form (USYS:USYSTXT) available with Uniface. The focus stays with the help window until the user uses either ^QUIT or ^ACCEPT or clicks the button on the USYS:USYSTXT form. At that point, control of the application is returned to the statement following the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span> statement.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__topic_d48307e1_d48308e1_d48309e1_d48310e1_d48311e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d251581e718\">Help on Windows</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73481e1_d73482e1_d73483e1\">The Microsoft Compressed HTML Help\n\t\t(<span class=\"ph filepath\">.chm</span>) can be displayed using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help/id</span> ProcScript command to\n\t\tstart the Microsoft HTML Help Viewer (<span class=\"ph filepath\">hh.exe</span>) with the specified numeric ID.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73484e1_d73485e1_d73486e1\">Microsoft also provides an SDK that enables you to\n            integrate the help more closely into your application. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms670169.aspx\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms670169.aspx</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__p_d73487e1_d73488e1_d73489e1\">The WinHelp format (<span class=\"ph filepath\">.hlp</span>) can be\n            called using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help/topic</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help/keyword</span>\n            ProcScript statements. Although it is an older format, you can download the Windows Help\n            executable for more supported Windows versions from Microsoft Support.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__section_rjt_wzg_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d251581e755\">Example: Calling Native Help</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example starts the native help engine and displays the\n            index from the help file identified by the logical name MYHELP:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__pre_jdf_xzg_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger help\nhelp/topic \" \", \"myhelp\"\nif ($status &lt; 0)\n message \"Unable to show help index: %%$status\"\nendif\nend ; end trigger\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__section_nxq_vzg_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d251581e767\">Example: Calling Uniface Help Message</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example displays the help text or message identified by\n            HELPTEXT. The example assumes that the appropriate <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span> and\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$variation</span> settings are used.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cfj1665702607852__pre_kyd_wzg_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger help\nhelp/noborder $text(HELPTEXT), 3,4,7,23\nend; help</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ano1665702607930.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Online Help for Uniface Applications</a><p>Uniface enables you to retrieve and display help topics, either using the native help system or Uniface help texts.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bxo1665702608169.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Implementing Online Help</a><p>How you call online help from Uniface depends on the format of the help file.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtf1665702608323.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$text</a><p>Return the text of a message or help text.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/viq1665702608478.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger help</a><p>Trigger for reacting to the user's request for online help in a desktop application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7435955\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7435955\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "help Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Version: Use up/down arrow keys to navigate, Esc to collapse. Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0 Reflection Desktop User Guide (German) Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German) Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1 Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Rocket Uniface Library 10.4 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.0 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.1 Reflection Desktop Benutzerhandbuch V17.1 Reflection FTP Scripting Guide (Deutsch) V17.0 Reflection Desktop User Guide (German) Secure Host Access FTP Client User Guide (German) Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.0 Reflection FTP Client User Guide (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Scripting (German) V21.1 Reflection FTP Command Reference (German) V21.1 Last Updated Okt 31, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Display help information, either a Uniface help message or information from the native help system. help ( /id | /topic | /keyword ) Parameters { /noborder } help { /noborder } HelpMessage { , VertPos , HorizPos { , VertSize , HorizSize }} help/id Topic , ChmFile help/topic Topic { , LogicalName } help/keyword Keyword { , LogicalName } Qualifiers Table 1. Qualifiers Qualifier Description /id Retrieves and displays an online help topic in a CHM file based on its numeric context ID. /topic Retrieves and displays an online help topic, index, or table of contents from the native help system. /keyword Retrieves and displays help about a keyword from a WinHelp file. Note: WinHelp is an obsolete help system. /noborder In character mode, displays the form window for USYS:USYSTXT without a border. The switch is ignored in GUI mode and in server page components. Parameters Table 2. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Topic String Help topic identifier. If Topic is an empty string (\"\"), the index or table of contents for the native help is displayed. LogicalName String Location of the help file as specified in the initialization file. If omitted or not found in the initialization file, the logical name DEFAULT is used. Keyword String Keyword that maps to a topic. If Keyword is an empty string (\"\") or is not found, the native help engine displays an error message. HelpMessage String Help message text. Often, the function $text is used, referring to a global help text or message. VertPos , HorizPos , VertSize , and HorizSize String Position and size of the help form, expressed in character cells. If the help text is larger than the size defined, vertical and horizontal scroll bars appear as needed. By default, the help window appears with a size that exactly fits the help text being displayed. These arguments have no effect in the Web environment. Return Values Table 3. Values Returned in $status Value Meaning 1 Uniface help form was exited with ^ACCEPT. 0 Native help successfully started. This value is always returned in the Web environment. Uniface help form was left with ^QUIT. -1 Uniface help form USYS:USYSTXT.frm could not be found. -2 Uniface help form is not correct. -3 Unable to start native help. -4 Platform does not support native help. (If this case you may want to use the help statement to provide help information.) -5 Native help does not support the requested option. -6 Unable to map logical name. -7 Requested topic or keyword not found. Table 4. Values commonly returned by $procerror following help Value Error Constant Meaning -350 <UHLPERR_STARTUP> Unable to start help. Uniface form USYS:USYSTXT.frm is missing or is not correct. -351 <UHLPERR_PLATFORM> Platform does not support native help. (In this case you may want to use the help [native] statement to provide help information.) -352 <UHLPERR_LOGICAL_NAME> Unable to map logical name. -354 <UHLPERR_OPTION> Native help does not support the requested option. -353 <UHLPERR_TOPIC> Requested help topic or keyword not found. Use Use in Form components. Description When used with the /id switch, the help statement starts the specified Microsoft Help file ( .chm ) and displays the help file corresponding to the context ID. When using this switch is used, an initialization file that maps the id to the topic must be provided in the same directory as the CHM file. When used with /topic , the help statement starts a native help engine to display the specified information. When used without a switch or with /noborders , the help statement displays the specified Uniface help text in an overlay help form (USYS:USYSTXT) available with Uniface. The focus stays with the help window until the user uses either ^QUIT or ^ACCEPT or clicks the button on the USYS:USYSTXT form. At that point, control of the application is returned to the statement following the help statement. Help on Windows The Microsoft Compressed HTML Help ( .chm ) can be displayed using the help/id ProcScript command to start the Microsoft HTML Help Viewer ( hh.exe ) with the specified numeric ID. Microsoft also provides an SDK that enables you to integrate the help more closely into your application. For more information, see msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms670169.aspx . The WinHelp format ( .hlp ) can be called using the help/topic and help/keyword ProcScript statements. Although it is an older format, you can download the Windows Help executable for more supported Windows versions from Microsoft Support. Example: Calling Native Help The following example starts the native help engine and displays the index from the help file identified by the logical name MYHELP: trigger help help/topic \" \", \"myhelp\" if ($status < 0) message \"Unable to show help index: %%$status\" endif end ; end trigger Copy Example: Calling Uniface Help Message The following example displays the help text or message identified by HELPTEXT. The example assumes that the appropriate $language and $variation settings are used. trigger help help/noborder $text(HELPTEXT), 3,4,7,23 end; help Copy Related Links Online Help for Uniface Applications Uniface enables you to retrieve and display help topics, either using the native help system or Uniface help texts. Implementing Online Help How you call online help from Uniface depends on the format of the help file. $text Return the text of a message or help text. trigger help Trigger for reacting to the user's request for online help in a desktop application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}